## TL;DR: What Every 4ct Elongated Cushion Buyer Must Know First

A 4 carat elongated cushion cut diamond ring pairs the most visually dramatic cushion size with the finger-lengthening geometry of a 1.15–1.25 L/W ratio, producing a ring that covers the finger from edge to edge at average ring sizes. Settings start at [$1,000 for the Petite Solitaire 14K White Gold](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/petite-solitaire-engagement-ring-item-194386?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational); the best entry complete build is an [IGI 4ct F-VS1 lab elongated cushion from $4,400](https://www.bluenile.com/diamond-search?shape=cushion&a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) plus the [Classic Four Prong Solitaire Platinum at $1,180](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/classic-four-prong-solitaire-engagement-ring-item-194156?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) for **from $5,580 total**. **→ Best first pick: IGI 4ct D-VVS1 lab elongated cushion at 1.20 L/W + [Classic Four Prong Solitaire Platinum at $1,180](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/classic-four-prong-solitaire-engagement-ring-item-194156?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) = from $6,980 total — the definitive 4ct elongated cushion solitaire build, D color and VVS1 clarity in platinum, targeting exactly the 1.20 ratio sweet spot.**

**The Empty Tier:** The natural 4ct elongated cushion category is one of the thinnest inventory segments in fine diamonds — at any given time, Blue Nile may carry fewer than 10 natural cushion diamonds above 4ct with L/W ratios in the 1.15–1.25 range that also meet reasonable cut quality standards. Natural supply at this carat weight and specific ratio combination is structurally limited; the market simply does not produce enough 4ct+ elongated cushion rough at premium ratios to build meaningful retail inventory. Lab grown diamonds have completely solved this problem — IGI-certified 4ct lab elongated cushions in D-VVS1 at 1.20 L/W are available year-round across multiple Blue Nile inventory price points.

