## 4ct Natural Elongated Cushion Diamond: Stone Data

Natural 4ct elongated cushion diamonds exist in Blue Nile's inventory but represent a structurally thin supply pool due to The Empty Tier. Buyers committed to natural origin should approach this category with patience and flexibility — the specific stone they want may not be in stock at the moment they shop, and waiting for inventory to refresh is often necessary. Natural elongated cushion diamonds at 4ct carry GIA certification, which is the authoritative natural diamond grading standard, and they carry the rarity premium associated with large-carat natural fancy shapes.

